'''''Geastrum australe''''' is an inedible species of [[mushroom]] belonging to the genus ''[[Geastrum]]'', or earthstar fungi. It can be mistaken for ''[[Geastrum saccatum]]'' or ''[[Geastrum simulans]]'', and is found in Melbourne.<ref>http://www.rbg.vic.gov.au/dbpages/cat/index.php/fungicatalogue/name/7685</ref>
